\ufeffTitle: Ida Lester's dresser. Everybody called her "Cousin Ida from Milwaukee." She was a burlesque dancer. She went to the Amsterdam Musical Association, every Saturday. Sometimes I would call early Saturday evening and she'd say, "Darlin', I'm sleeping ..."
